history.content:
Hi there,
There have been a lot of communications about enrolling in CS 47B for the fall 2018 from CS-intended transfers and others. Those who plan to complete CS 47B must consult with Carol Marshall at carolm@cs.berkeley.edu. Carol runs the CS Self Paced Center, which administers CS47B. The process of enrolling in the course entails determining which assignments/projects/exams must be completed, after which Carol will provide a permission code.
Currently, Carol is out of the office and not available by email. She will be available after July 31. Please be patient. You should be able to enroll in this course, so please don't worry about this.
Should you have other questions about schedule planning for the fall, please email CS Advising at cs-advising@cs.berkeley.edu.
Thank you!
